        "# Getting Started: Installing the Libraries\n",
        "\n",
        "Before diving into code, you'll need to install two essential libraries. Open your command prompt or terminal and type:\n",
        "\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "pip install PyPDF2==1.26.0\n",
